        <strong>Total additional training per season: 81.9 hours</strong></p>

        <p>My sons get <strong>nearly 82 extra hours of focused ball work per season</strong> compared to their teammates who only attend team practice. That&#8217;s equivalent to 82 one-hour private training sessions&#8212;or about $8,200 worth of private coaching at $100/hour.</p>

        <p>And it costs us $0 beyond the Anytime Soccer Training subscription.</p>
